name: Trivia Contest
originalText:
Visit — An opponent chooses colorless card, creature card, or plane, then mills a card. You have ten seconds to name something from the chosen category that starts with the same letter as the milled card. If you do, claim the prize
Prize — You get {Ticket}{Ticket}{Ticket}, then you may put a sticker on a nonland permanent you own. Sacrifice Trivia Contest and open an Attraction.
